{"tid":55542,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE 免費資源分享","createTime":"2016-12-26T13:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T13:26:05.000Z","uid":70025,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"929c29a32deafd85966a6dd7f2f5edb632f84ead","tid":55542,"uid":70025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"仲有三個月就考DSE，好想響度同大家講聲加油！我都係2017DSE考生，我都明科科都補習會好貴，響度想分享幾個免費學到野既方法：<br />\n<br />\n1. 瘋狂去試堂<br />\n依家d補習社咪好鍾意搞d免費試堂，而d導師為左留住學生都會擺d勁野出黎教。例如我之前中文都去左winter、ben fung、蕭源d試堂，都學到好多野。雖然咁樣做有d唔好意思，不過佢地搞得試堂都預左有d學生上完會唔報&hellip;&hellip;咁咪當幫下我地d貧苦學生囉<br />\n<br />\n2. 睇唔同學術IG<br />\n我想講其實玩IG都可以學到DSE野，唔一定係得個玩字。例如 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tutor.box\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftutor.box&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d6fd3eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tutor.box</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mathman.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmathman.hk&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=954c6cd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/mathman.hk</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/onedayonemc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fonedayonemc&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=09c16ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/onedayonemc</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/dse.chinese.kingdom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdse.chinese.kingdom&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ec2094a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/dse.chinese.kingdom</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/dseenglish\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdseenglish&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=736a1906\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/dseenglish</a> <br />\n呢d我都會成日去睇。當然如果大家有其他學術IG都不妨講出黎，等大家唔洗比錢補習都可以學下唔同科既野<br />\n<br />\n3. 上Youtube睇教學分享<br />\n有好多小型導師都會上網拍片，分享DSE心得。例如：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJ29RUajHhET4mPA-hyxesQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCJ29RUajHhET4mPA-hyxesQ&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a19a94b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJ29RUajHhET4mPA-hyxesQ</a>  7個5**女狀元<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/SimonLamCL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FSimonLamCL&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=35666115\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/SimonLamCL</a>  十大優青Victor<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQTUvTm-DlXAHo8MiaIdvGw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCQTUvTm-DlXAHo8MiaIdvGw&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=54153956\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQTUvTm-DlXAHo8MiaIdvGw</a> Function Tong<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/HermanTCN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FHermanTCN&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7c276712\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/HermanTCN</a>  Herman To Math<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2LTVe8LozEWJat0P_LItAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC2LTVe8LozEWJat0P_LItAQ&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=286ca5d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2LTVe8LozEWJat0P_LItAQ</a>  Jason So Chinese<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfNe6AMdgT3be1PopBPhiQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCfNe6AMdgT3be1PopBPhiQA&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1c44692a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfNe6AMdgT3be1PopBPhiQA</a>   Leung Sir [DSE] 中文教室<br />\n<br />\n數學仲有神級Herman Yeung<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/hyhermanyeung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fhyhermanyeung&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4f6c7513\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/hyhermanyeung</a> <br />\n<br />\n睇曬呢d教學片，其實都已經唔洗去補習了。<br />\n<br />\n當然我都知要做齊以上咁多樣野都係好浪費時間，同埋學既野會唔夠齊全。不過老老實實，無錢就係要付出比其他人多既時間。同埋其實唔係每科都要補架嘛，咁揀返自己比較需要補習既科黎試堂/睇片/睇IG咪得囉。<br />\n<br />\n希望以上分享幫到其他DSE同路人啦！ 加油！ 頂硬上！"},{"pid":"8238ac502d85869906eb022c2b24330b8345b5ad","tid":55542,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5e5f90ebf18c522fd2e2f90420c426d3db7fa0eb","tid":55542,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"Herman yeung&gt;Herman to唔知咩<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"652a2d115d10d66282d341013542b88357717949","tid":55542,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:21:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"141a8973f2b3ebb8a17c3191b6a704ef185c08bb","tid":55542,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0d1729edb6a5989b0c3a4cfc52ff755eb0bc5f6","tid":55542,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86ccc60a8553d87f6749fc69d739bf592ba7c9f","tid":55542,"uid":49093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好心樓主dse雞就返去溫書啦<br />\n自私啲咁講 分享比你啲對手又冇著數<br />\n<br />\n利申 asso仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果樓主係擾敵撚 當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能係打手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bu